      • getURIbyName

        public final URI getURIbyName(String stanzaName)
        Returns the URI, i.e. the Sequence Ontology namespace URL followed by an ID of an sequence ontology term, of the stanza whose name matches the given name. If multiple matches are found, only the first matching one is returned.
        Parameters:
        stanzaName - the given stanza name
        Returns:
        the URI of the given sequence ontology name, or null if no match is found.

      • getURIbyId

        public final URI getURIbyId(String stanzaId)

        Parameters:
        stanzaId - the given stanzaId
        Returns:
        the created URI
